main(String[]) - Static method in class launcher.Main
Calls all other methods to get metadata from all files of specified type and create html table with relevant info from the files metadata Resulting html table is based on a model html file Paths must include separator at the end
Main - Class in launcher
This class servers as the launcher for the java application Some predefined fields are present and were used in testing, can be changed later
Main() - Constructor for class launcher.Main
 
MetaDataExtractor - Class in extractor
This class uses some methods to: -List all files of a specific type that exist in a directory; -Extract each file's metadata; -Create a String to populate an html table with specific info from each file's metadata -Create a new html (table.html) file from a pre-existing template called tableModel.html with populated html table
MetaDataExtractor() - Constructor for class extractor.MetaDataExtractor
 
metadataToHtml(String, String, String) - Method in class extractor.MetaDataExtractor
Get relevant information from the metadata of each file on specified path and build an html table with that information Resulting html table is based on a model html file Paths must include separator at the end
